Złożoność pamięciowa i obliczeniowa¶

In [128]:
mean_time_power = Float64[]
mean_memory_power = Int64[]
mean_time_jacobi = Float64[]
mean_memory_jacobi = Int64[]
mean_time_jacobi_B = Float64[]
mean_memory_jacobi_B = Int64[]
mean_time_qr = Float64[]
mean_memory_qr = Int64[]
mean_time_qr_h = Float64[]
mean_memory_qr_h = Int64[]
mean_time_qr_s = Float64[]
mean_memory_qr_s = Int64[]
mean_time_qr_s_h = Float64[]
mean_memory_qr_s_h = Int64[]

i_values = 2:2:22

for i in i_values
    A = randn(i,i)
    A = A * A'
    
    xbench = @benchmark power_method(A, 100)
    append!(mean_time_power, mean(xbench).time)
    append!(mean_memory_power, mean(xbench).memory)
    
    xbench = @benchmark jacobi_A(A, 100)
    append!(mean_time_jacobi, mean(xbench).time)
    append!(mean_memory_jacobi, mean(xbench).memory)
    
    xbench = @benchmark jacobi_B(A, 100)
    append!(mean_time_jacobi_B, mean(xbench).time)
    append!(mean_memory_jacobi_B, mean(xbench).memory)
    
    xbench = @benchmark QR_eigen(A, 100)
    append!(mean_time_qr, mean(xbench).time)
    append!(mean_memory_qr, mean(xbench).memory)
    
    xbench = @benchmark QR_eigen_hessen(A, 100)
    append!(mean_time_qr_h, mean(xbench).time)
    append!(mean_memory_qr_h, mean(xbench).memory)
    
    xbench = @benchmark shiftQRc(A, 100)
    append!(mean_time_qr_s, mean(xbench).time)
    append!(mean_memory_qr_s, mean(xbench).memory)
    
    xbench = @benchmark shiftQRc_hessen(A, 100)
    append!(mean_time_qr_s_h, mean(xbench).time)
    append!(mean_memory_qr_s_h, mean(xbench).memory)
    
    println(i)
end
